description: Are you starting your day the cranky way? No worries, all us coffee junkies have certainly “bean” there.  Thankfully, the Serene Caffeine Coffee House can intervene. The delicious coffee from this eco-friendly trailer will surely lift your mood, and since it’s a low-acid brew, it’s happens to be a pretty healthy option for you. For fresh hot coffee, teas, and a few tasty treats...be sure to look out for the queenly Serene Caffeine Coffee House on the streets.
name: Serene Caffeine
